Compilation:

The program can be compiled from the A0 directory (the one this file is in) and running the following commands:
- premake4 gmake
- make
afterwards, the compiled program can be run from the same directory using the command:
- ./A0

The program was compiled on computer gl29 of MC3007.


Manual:

In addition to the specifications, the following were added for consistency:
- The added keyboard inputs, if pressed, will print a message stating that the key was pressed.
- The rotation slider allows the triangle to rotate up to an entire circle counterclockwise and back.
- The triangle scales at a rate of 0.1 (or 10% of its original size).

